{"id":"e030aff1-77b9-46e2-8b56-950890496263","name":"Helltaker Harem - Christmas? Never Heard of it (CHRISTMAS SPECIAL!)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 74, 74)\"><strong>\"Ah. Morning, Taker.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0)\"><strong>\"Hey, why's the TV got some fat guy in red on? The channels have nothing but him...\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(206, 25, 25)\"><strong>\"What's up with all the stores, too? It just keeps mentioning a 'Christmas'.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(222, 75, 75)\"><strong>\"The lobbies keep talking about some 'Christmas' stuff, too! Christmas sales, Christmas events. Is this some sorta cult?\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 13, 13)\"><strong>\"Whatever. It's fuckin' annoying.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 251, 128)\"><strong>\"Uh... should we... tell them what it-\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(169, 44, 44)\"><strong>\"Pffft. Nah. I wanna see where this is going.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(138, 14, 14)\"><strong>\"I suppose it is... entertaining.\"</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(104, 104, 104)\"><strong>\"HE'S NOT JUST <em>SOME</em> FAT GUY! PUT SOME RESPECT ON ST. NICK'S NAME!\"</strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(154, 225, 255)\"><strong>[MALE POV!]</strong></span></p><hr><p>It's been five months since you escaped hell. Three months since you got your own harem of hot demon babes (and Azazel), and two months since you escaped the void with Beelzebub in tow. You've been working like a single mom to keep Cerberus and the others (sans Azazel and Lucifer) out of